{%- comment -%}
  QDM · Manifiesto — Página editorial
  Orden: imagen header → título/subtítulo centrado → foto (margen) →
  bloque texto-izq/foto-der → bloque foto-izq/texto-der → foto (margen)
  → texto de cierre centrado → CTA
{%- endcomment -%}

<article class="qdm-manifesto">

  {%- if section.settings.header_image != blank -%}
    <div class="qdm-manifesto__header-image-band">
      {{
        section.settings.header_image
        | image_url: width: 1600
        | image_tag:
          loading: 'eager',
          fetchpriority: 'high',
          class: 'qdm-manifesto__header-image',
          widths: '600, 900, 1200, 1600',
          sizes: '100vw',
          alt: section.settings.header_image.alt | default: 'QDM · Manifiesto'
      }}
    </div>
  {%- endif -%}

  <header class="qdm-manifesto__header">
    <div class="qdm-manifesto__inner qdm-manifesto__inner--center">
      <nav class="qdm-manifesto__breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="{{ routes.root_url }}" class="qdm-manifesto__bc-link">QDM</a>
        <span class="qdm-manifesto__bc-sep" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
        <span class="qdm-manifesto__bc-current">{{ section.settings.breadcrumb | default: 'Qué Diría Mi Madre' | upcase }}</span>
      </nav>
      <h1 class="qdm-manifesto__title">{{ section.settings.title | default: 'Manifiesto' }}</h1>
      {%- if section.settings.subtitle != blank -%}
        <p class="qdm-manifesto__subtitle">{{ section.settings.subtitle }}</p>
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>
  </header>

  {%- if section.settings.photo_1 != blank -%}
    <div class="qdm-manifesto__photo-margined">
      {{
        section.settings.photo_1
        | image_url: width: 1400
        | image_tag:
          loading: 'lazy',
          class: 'qdm-manifesto__photo-margined-img',
          widths: '600, 900, 1200, 1400',
          sizes: '(min-width: 768px) 90vw, 100vw',
          alt: section.settings.photo_1.alt | default: 'QDM · Manifiesto'
      }}
    </div>
  {%- endif -%}

  {%- if section.settings.split_1_text != blank or section.settings.split_1_image != blank -%}
    <div class="qdm-manifesto__split">
      <div class="qdm-manifesto__split-text">
        <div class="qdm-manifesto__prose">{{ section.settings.split_1_text }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="qdm-manifesto__split-media">
        {%- if section.settings.split_1_image != blank -%}
          {{
            section.settings.split_1_image
            | image_url: width: 900
            | image_tag:
              loading: 'lazy',
              class: 'qdm-manifesto__split-img',
              widths: '400, 600, 800, 900',
              sizes: '(min-width: 768px) 45vw, 100vw',
              alt: section.settings.split_1_image.alt | default: 'QDM · Manifiesto'
          }}
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>
    </div>
  {%- endif -%}

  {%- if section.settings.split_2_text != blank or section.settings.split_2_image != blank -%}
    <div class="qdm-manifesto__split qdm-manifesto__split--reverse">
      <div class="qdm-manifesto__split-media">
        {%- if section.settings.split_2_image != blank -%}
          {{
            section.settings.split_2_image
            | image_url: width: 900
            | image_tag:
              loading: 'lazy',
              class: 'qdm-manifesto__split-img',
              widths: '400, 600, 800, 900',
              sizes: '(min-width: 768px) 45vw, 100vw',
              alt: section.settings.split_2_image.alt | default: 'QDM · Manifiesto'
          }}
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>
      <div class="qdm-manifesto__split-text">
        <div class="qdm-manifesto__prose">{{ section.settings.split_2_text }}</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  {%- endif -%}

  {%- if section.settings.photo_2 != blank -%}
    <div class="qdm-manifesto__photo-margined">
      {{
        section.settings.photo_2
        | image_url: width: 1400
        | image_tag:
          loading: 'lazy',
          class: 'qdm-manifesto__photo-margined-img',
          widths: '600, 900, 1200, 1400',
          sizes: '(min-width: 768px) 90vw, 100vw',
          alt: section.settings.photo_2.alt | default: 'QDM · Manifiesto'
      }}
    </div>
  {%- endif -%}

  {%- if section.settings.closing_text != blank -%}
    <div class="qdm-manifesto__block">
      <div class="qdm-manifesto__inner qdm-manifesto__inner--center">
        <div class="qdm-manifesto__prose">{{ section.settings.closing_text }}</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  {%- endif -%}

  {%- if section.settings.cta_label != blank -%}
    <div class="qdm-manifesto__cta-wrap">
      <div class="qdm-manifesto__inner qdm-manifesto__inner--center">
        <a
          href="{{ section.settings.cta_url | default: routes.collections_url }}"
          class="qdm-manifesto__cta"
        >
          {{ section.settings.cta_label | escape }} →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  {%- endif -%}

</article>

{% stylesheet %}
  .qdm-manifesto {
    background-color: var(--qdm-cream, #fffef7);
    padding-block-end: 5rem;
  }

  .qdm-manifesto__inner {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    padding-inline: 1.5rem;
  }

  .qdm-manifesto__inner--center {
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* ── Header image (hero) ── */
  .qdm-manifesto__header-image-band {
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .qdm-manifesto__header-image {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .qdm-manifesto__header-image {
      aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    }
  }

  /* ── Header — centrado en desktop y mobile ── */
  .qdm-manifesto__header {
    padding-block: 2.5rem 0;
  }

  .qdm-manifesto__breadcrumb {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-family: var(--qdm-font-body, 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: rgba(38, 37, 34, 0.4);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .qdm-manifesto__bc-link {
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 200ms ease;
  }

  @media (hover: hover) {
    .qdm-manifesto__bc-link:hover {
      color: var(--qdm-carbon, #262522);
    }
  }

  .qdm-manifesto__bc-sep {
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
  }

  .qdm-manifesto__bc-current {
    color: rgba(38, 37, 34, 0.55);
  }

  .qdm-manifesto__title {
    font-family: var(--qdm-font-heading, 'Work Sans', sans-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 9vw, 3.75rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: var(--qdm-carbon, #262522);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .qdm-manifesto__subtitle {
    font-family: var(--qdm-font-body, 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: rgba(38, 37, 34, 0.6);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── Body blocks ── */
  .qdm-manifesto__block {
    padding-block-start: 2.5rem;
  }

  .qdm-manifesto__prose p {
    font-family: var(--qdm-font-body, 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--qdm-carbon, #262522);
    margin: 0 0 0.875rem;
  }

  .qdm-manifesto__prose p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* ── Foto con margen (no full-bleed, no tan explotada como el header) ── */
  .qdm-manifesto__photo-margined {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    margin-block-start: 3rem;
    padding-inline: 1.5rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .qdm-manifesto__photo-margined-img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  /* ── Bloques intercalados: texto + foto en columnas (desktop) ── */
  .qdm-manifesto__split {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 3rem;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    margin-block-start: 3.5rem;
    padding-inline: 1.5rem;
  }

  .qdm-manifesto__split-media {
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .qdm-manifesto__split-img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  /* ── CTA ── */
  .qdm-manifesto__cta-wrap {
    padding-block-start: 3rem;
  }

  .qdm-manifesto__cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    font-family: var(--qdm-font-body, 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--qdm-carbon, #262522);
    background-color: var(--qdm-amber, #ebb86e);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--qdm-amber, #ebb86e);
    padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition:
      background-color 200ms ease,
      border-color 200ms ease;
    -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
  }

  @media (hover: hover) {
    .qdm-manifesto__cta:hover {
      background-color: var(--qdm-camel, #c9a787);
      border-color: var(--qdm-camel, #c9a787);
    }
  }

  /* ── Mobile: todo apilado, sin reordenar columnas ── */
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .qdm-manifesto__header {
      padding-block-start: 2rem;
    }

    .qdm-manifesto__block {
      padding-block-start: 2rem;
    }

    .qdm-manifesto__photo-margined {
      margin-block-start: 2.5rem;
      padding-inline: 1rem;
    }

    .qdm-manifesto__split {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-block-start: 2.5rem;
      padding-inline: 1.5rem;
    }

    .qdm-manifesto__split-img {
      aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    }

    .qdm-manifesto__cta-wrap {
      padding-block-start: 2.5rem;
    }

    .qdm-manifesto {
      padding-block-end: 4rem;
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .qdm-manifesto__cta {
      transition: none;
    }
  }
{% endstylesheet %}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "QDM · Manifiesto",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "shopify-section",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Encabezado"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "header_image",
      "label": "Imagen de encabezado",
      "info": "Foto editorial (equipo/fundadoras). Se muestra arriba de todo, full-bleed."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "breadcrumb",
      "label": "Breadcrumb — segundo nivel",
      "default": "Qué Diría Mi Madre"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "title",
      "label": "Título",
      "default": "Manifiesto"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "subtitle",
      "label": "Subtítulo",
      "default": "El alma de lo que hacemos."
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Foto 1"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "photo_1",
      "label": "Imagen",
      "info": "Ancho casi completo, con margen a los costados (no full-bleed)."
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Bloque intercalado 1 — texto izquierda / foto derecha"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "split_1_text",
      "label": "Texto",
      "default": "<p>Nace como una respuesta al «qué dirán».</p><p>Una reivindicación de la libertad de ser uno mismo.</p><p>De hacer lo que uno desea. De mostrarse tal como es.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "split_1_image",
      "label": "Imagen"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Bloque intercalado 2 — foto izquierda / texto derecha"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "split_2_image",
      "label": "Imagen"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "split_2_text",
      "label": "Texto",
      "default": "<p>Creamos piezas originales que no siguen tendencias: cuentan historias.</p><p>Cada diseño nace con intención, carácter y una identidad propia.</p><p>No trabajamos con grandes volúmenes. Elegimos la curaduría antes que la cantidad.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Foto 2"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "photo_2",
      "label": "Imagen",
      "info": "Centrada, mismo margen que Foto 1."
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Cierre"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "closing_text",
      "label": "Texto de cierre",
      "default": "<p>Creemos que aquello que forma parte de nuestra identidad merece ser celebrado.</p><p>QDM es un lugar para todas las personas que encuentran en una joya una forma de hablar de sí mismas.</p><p>Porque creemos que la individualidad nunca debería esconderse. Debería poder llevarse puesta.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "CTA"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "cta_label",
      "label": "Texto del botón",
      "default": "Explorar la colección"
    },
    {
      "type": "url",
      "id": "cta_url",
      "label": "URL del botón"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "QDM · Manifiesto"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
